Fictional texts or texts from the humanities are translated from French into Estonian and vice-versa. Texts are analysed from lexical, stilistic and pragmatic point of view in order to take these aspects into account during the translation process. The translations are discussed together with the students, paying special attention to different possibilities in the translations.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To give basic knowledge about translation from French into Estonian/ from Estonian into FrenchLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student who has attended the course: 1) is able to translate with a dictionary easier texts from French into Estonian (fictional, humanities); 2) is able to translate with a dictionary easier texts from Estonian into French; 3) is able to use dictionaries and other relevant sources of information.
